## Key Distinction — Baked In vs Bolted On

| Approach | Physical Understanding | Gap to Reality |
|----------|----------------------|----------------|
| Mathematical simulation | Approximated | Always present |
| Constitution/constraints | Described | Large |
| Separate physics module | Consulted | Latency + failure modes |
| **This system** | **Inherited from foundation** | **Minimal — trained on reality** |

